#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.48:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga"
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Ādiccasutta"
msgstr "48. The Sun"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.101"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.48:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ādiccassa, bhikkhave, udayato etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, "
"yadidaṃ—aruṇuggaṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, the dawn is the forerunner and precursor of the sunrise."

msgctxt "sn46.48:1.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ uppādāya etaṃ "
"pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, for a mendicant good friendship is the forerunner and "
"precursor of the arising of the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.48:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—satta bojjhaṅge "
"bhāvessati, satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with good friends can expect to develop and cultivate the seven "
"awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.48:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti, satta "
"bojjhaṅge bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the seven "
"awakening factors?"

msgctxt "sn46.48:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "sn46.48:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti, satta "
"bojjhaṅge bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the seven "
"awakening factors.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.48:1.7"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
